## Requirements

- [Node](https://nodejs.org/en/)
- [Yarn](https://yarnpkg.com/en/docs/install)
- [Elm](http://elm-lang.org/)
- [elm-test](https://github.com/elm-community/elm-test)

## Local development

To install dependencies

    yarn bootstrap

To run app locally

    yarn dev

To run tests

    yarn test

To run tests with file watching

    yarn watch
